snippet: Yani Tseng moved into position to end a long victory drought, shooting a nine-under 63 to take a three-stroke lead into the final round of the Safeway Classic in Portland, Ore.
abstract: Yani Tseng takes third-round lead in LPGA's Safeway Classic in Portland, Ore; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Yani Tseng moved into position to end a long victory drought, shooting a nine-under 63 to take a three-stroke lead into the final round of the Safeway Classic in Portland, Ore.

headline.main: Tseng Opens Three-Shot Lead in Oregon
